Argued and submitted June 9, 2016, affirmed June 14, 2017 GUSTAVO CONDE SOTO, Petitioner-Appellant, v. STATE OF OREGON, Defendant-Respondent.

Yamhill County Circuit Court

CV110756; A157523 395 P3d 959 John E. Storkel argued the cause and filed the brief for appellant. Paul L. Smith, Deputy Solicitor General, argued the cause for respondent. With him on the brief was Ellen F. Rosenblum, Attorney General. Before Duncan, Presiding Judge, and DeVore, Judge, and Garrett, Judge*

Garrett, J., vice Flynn, J. pro tempore.

 PER CURIAM

Affirmed. Chavez v. State of Oregon, 283 Or App 788, 391 P3d 801 (2017).
